<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id8ebcc25c-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s285b"><num value="285b">§ 285b.</num><heading> Coordination of policies and operations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The policies and operations of the representatives of the United States on the Bank shall be coordinated with other United States policies in such manner as the President shall direct.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id8ebcc25d-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">(<ref href="/us/pl/89/369/s4">Pub. L. 89–369, § 4</ref>, <date date="1966-03-16">Mar. 16, 1966</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/80/71">80 Stat. 71</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/101/240/tV/s541/d/2">Pub. L. 101–240, title V, § 541(d)(2)</ref>, (f)(3), <date date="1989-12-19">Dec. 19, 1989</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/103/2518">103 Stat. 2518</ref>, 2519.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id8ebcc25e-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id8ebcc25f-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id8ebcc260-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1989—<ref href="/us/pl/101/240">Pub. L. 101–240</ref> struck out subsec. (a) designation and struck out subsec. (b) which read as follows: “An annual report with respect to United States participation in the Bank shall be submitted to the Congress by such agency or officer as the President shall designate.”</p>
</note>
</notes>
</section>
